{"image_id": "NSC_2013_page_28", "image_size": [1257, 1632], "ocr": [{"text": "K22", "bbox": [608.9, 1530.0, 654.2, 1555.4]}, {"text": "SUMMARIZED RESULTS OF OPERATIONS", "bbox": [103.3, 120.9, 581.5, 146.3]}, {"text": "2013 Compared with 2012", "bbox": [103.3, 173.7, 365.8, 199.2]}, {"text": "Net income in 2013 was $1.9 billion, or $6.04 per diluted share, up $161 million, or 9%, compared with", "bbox": [103.3, 226.0, 1063.5, 251.4]}, {"text": "$1.7 billion, or $5.37 per diluted share, in 2012, a reflection of a 4% increase in income from railway operations,", "bbox": [103.3, 252.2, 1144.1, 277.7]}, {"text": "in addition to the favorable impact of the recognition of the gain from the sale of certain assets to the Michigan", "bbox": [103.3, 278.5, 1126.0, 303.9]}, {"text": "Department of Transportation (MDOT), which benefited net income by $60 million and earnings per share by", "bbox": [103.3, 305.0, 1117.9, 330.5]}, {"text": "$0.19.  Railway operating revenues rose 2%, while operating expenses increased 1%, driven largely by higher", "bbox": [103.3, 331.3, 1118.4, 356.7]}, {"text": "volume-related expenses.", "bbox": [103.3, 357.8, 342.1, 383.2]}, {"text": "2012 Compared with 2011", "bbox": [103.3, 410.8, 365.8, 436.3]}, {"text": "Net income in 2012 was $1.7 billion, or $5.37 per diluted share, down $167 million, or 9%, compared with", "bbox": [103.3, 463.1, 1097.1, 488.5]}, {"text": "$1.9 billion, or $5.45 per diluted share, in 2011.  The decrease in net income was due to lower income from", "bbox": [103.3, 489.6, 1095.4, 515.0]}, {"text": "railway operations, lower nonoperating income items, higher interest expense on debt, and a higher effective", "bbox": [103.3, 515.9, 1105.9, 541.4]}, {"text": "income tax rate (Note 3).  Railway operating revenues decreased modestly, $132 million, reflecting lower average", "bbox": [103.3, 542.2, 1156.1, 567.6]}, {"text": "revenue per unit, including fuel surcharges.  Railway operating expenses also decreased modestly, $43 million,", "bbox": [103.3, 568.7, 1128.1, 594.1]}, {"text": "largely driven by the absence of the $58 million unfavorable arbitration ruling in 2011 and declines related to", "bbox": [103.3, 594.9, 1112.2, 620.4]}, {"text": "network efficiency and productivity gains, offset by higher depreciation and intermodal volume-related expenses.", "bbox": [103.3, 621.4, 1151.2, 646.9]}, {"text": "DETAILED RESULTS OF OPERATIONS", "bbox": [103.3, 674.7, 540.1, 700.2]}, {"text": "Railway Operating Revenues", "bbox": [103.3, 727.2, 399.9, 752.7]}, {"text": "Railway operating revenues were $11.2 billion in 2013, $11.0 billion in 2012, and $11.2 billion in 2011.  The", "bbox": [103.3, 779.5, 1113.0, 805.0]}, {"text": "following table presents a three-year comparison of revenues, volumes, and average revenue per unit by market", "bbox": [103.3, 806.0, 1132.3, 831.5]}, {"text": "group.", "bbox": [103.3, 832.3, 174.1, 857.8]}, {"text": "Revenues", "bbox": [428.1, 888.6, 517.8, 911.6]}, {"text": "Units", "bbox": [725.0, 888.6, 777.7, 911.6]}, {"text": "Revenue per Unit", "bbox": [948.9, 888.6, 1110.5, 911.6]}, {"text": "2013", "bbox": [355.2, 915.6, 402.2, 938.6]}, {"text": "2012", "bbox": [449.6, 915.6, 496.5, 938.6]}, {"text": "2011", "bbox": [543.9, 915.6, 590.8, 938.6]}, {"text": "2013", "bbox": [636.7, 915.6, 683.6, 938.6]}, {"text": "2012", "bbox": [727.8, 915.6, 774.7, 938.6]}, {"text": "2011", "bbox": [819.1, 915.6, 866.0, 938.6]}, {"text": "2013", "bbox": [911.9, 915.6, 958.9, 938.6]}, {"text": "2012", "bbox": [1006.3, 915.6, 1053.2, 938.6]}, {"text": "2011", "bbox": [1100.6, 915.6, 1147.5, 938.6]}, {"text": "($ in millions)", "bbox": [403.5, 942.1, 542.7, 965.1]}, {"text": "(in thousands)", "bbox": [678.5, 942.1, 824.4, 965.1]}, {"text": "($ per unit)", "bbox": [966.4, 942.1, 1092.8, 965.1]}, {"text": "Coal", "bbox": [97.0, 996.2, 141.5, 1019.1]}, {"text": "$  2,543  $  2,879  $  3,458   1,346.7   1,414.1   1,619.6  $  1,888  $  2,036  $  2,135", "bbox": [336.2, 996.2, 1165.5, 